    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，根节点是Project Manager，四个一级分支。任务管理这边具体要展开哪些功能点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Task Management"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "任务管理下面放四个：创建和分配任务、截止日期和提醒、子任务清单，还有一个拖拽调整优先级。拖拽这个交互挺重要的，要突出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create and assign tasks",
        "Due dates and reminders",
        "Subtask checklists",
        "Drag-and-drop priority"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，任务管理分支已添加。协作这块你之前提过实时评论和@提及，还有别的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Collaboration",
        "Real-time comments",
        "@mentions and notifications"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "协作再加文件附件和活动动态流。报表这块需要燃尽图和速度跟踪，还要能导出PDF。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "File attachments",
        "Activity feed",
        "Reporting",
        "Burndown charts",
